+Twigg:</b> The Government set out their strategy for the
+Railway in the Future of Rail White Paper published in July 2004. This
+new strategy is designed to control costs, improve reliability and
+deliver sufficient capacity to meet forecast
+demand.</p><p><a name="060518138000225"><b><a name="060518138001063">Mr.
+Carmichael:</b> To ask the Secretary of State
+for Transport whether <i>(a)</i> he and <i>(b)</i> his officials
